#. [message]: speaker=Goblin Scout
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios/04_Descending_into_Darkness.cfg:450
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios_old/04_Descending_into_Darkness.cfg:450
msgid "Attack!"
